s=\"citation\" id=\"114555\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114555)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114555)\">D&amp;C 78:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114812\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114812)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114812)\">D&amp;C 88:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114437\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114437)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114437)\">D&amp;C 76:51<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106327\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106327)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106327)\">Deut. 28:62<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106391\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106391)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106391)\">1 Sam. 12:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107414\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107414)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107414)\">Jer. 42:13-18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107574\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107574)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107574)\">Dan. 9:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">22. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108176\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108176)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108176)\">Matt. 23:33<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115758\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115758)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115758)\">D&amp;C 121:23<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">23. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106300\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106300)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106300)\">Deut. 11:28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114082\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114082)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114082)\">D&amp;C 58:30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114122\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114122)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114122)\">D&amp;C 59:21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">24. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108320\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108320)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108320)\">Mark 3:35<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">25. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111200\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111200)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111200)\">2 Ne. 9:41<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111541\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111541)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111541)\">Mosiah 3:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112237\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112237)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112237)\">Alma 38:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112436\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112436)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112436)\">Hel. 5:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">26. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111316\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111316)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111316)\">2 Ne. 31:4-21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">27. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110938\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 